      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;assignment-76-capstone-project-work-day-checkpoint-prepare&#34;&gt;Assignment 7.6: Capstone Project Work Day Checkpoint (Prepare)&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;goal&#34;&gt;Goal&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Show progress on your Creative Project by building the basic structure of your program.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;instructions&#34;&gt;Instructions&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Open your project proposal from Assignment 7.5.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Begin coding the structure of your project:&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Create variables, lists, or dictionaries you will need.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Write at least one function.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Add placeholder code (e.g., &lt;code&gt;print(&amp;quot;TODO: add game loop&amp;quot;)&lt;/code&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Make sure at least &lt;strong&gt;one feature&lt;/strong&gt; of your program works by the end of class (e.g., a menu, one chatbot response, a random choice, or a loop).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Save your progress and upload your &lt;code&gt;.py&lt;/code&gt; file to Canvas.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;Example&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-python&#34; data-lang=&#34;python&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; random&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;menu&lt;/span&gt;():&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    print(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Welcome to my random story generator!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    choice &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; input(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Press Enter to continue...&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    print(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;TODO: add story options here&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;menu()&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;challenge&#34;&gt;Challenge&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Add user input and one working response.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Comment your code to explain what each part will do.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;rubric&#34;&gt;Rubric&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Code includes project structure (30%)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; At least one working feature implemented (40%)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Code is saved and uploaded (20%)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Bonus for creativity or extra detail (10%)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
